# Raw, quoted, escaped, and multiline strings
..
    raw Human-readable text
    hash # this is data, not an inline comment
    marker_dots ..
    marker_colon :
    marker_bar |
    padded "  spaces are preserved  "
    escaped "first line\nsecond line\tindented"
    multilingual Dobrý deň — こんにちは
    paragraph|
        Multiline text keeps internal newlines.
        A # character here is also data.
